list.name: Default
list.comment: - Version: 1.1.6: Ability to resolve DTO objects by an expression of parameter in @DtoExtend section

task.summary: - Versions & artifact coordinates fixed - README updated

- Improved NPE handling by the DTO getters - Generation kit extended with an ability to generate parametrized synthetic fields in the result DTO class - Improved domain class interfaces handling: now all of them would be inherited by the DTO class, except of those who is marked by @DtoExclude - Handling of @DtoInclude(ID) on the collection fields implemented (including the conversion logic)

- Version 1.1.2 -> 1.1.3 - Added some unit tests to check the correctness of generated classes - Fixing issue #11 (if no type information provided as a value of targetEntity for JPA relation (one-to-many, many-to-many, etc., then the list generic value would be used )
- Little fix (removed break left after switch{} construction )
